lor: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"46c39d4f9084120827768192326a9aad677a4102","tid":1750744,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"嗰日都冇200萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a6dbaf4062c89c3433cbdd36e9fbcbbb0f1a8","tid":1750744,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n咪再講廢話"},{"pid":"debb5454814c482580ab3c23b5ab46b62d483c22","tid":1750744,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"應該 55開 頂盡 贏個馬鼻<br />\n275萬人投左票 黃既票數暫時應該有 130-140萬左右<br />\n200萬人遊行 最少有20-30萬未夠秤 再有d係打卡/射落海<br />\n計落條數真係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e496f8b63653b264e6711baeb7a0cc8d84080f","tid":1750744,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"咪再講廢話啦<br />\n不如諗下點樣拖屋企件廢老去投票好過啦<br />\n自己屋企人都未搞得掂。"}]}